               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>I) ዳዊት, Psalter (fols. <locus from="1r" to="130vb"/>)I-<locus target="#1"/>) መዝሙረ፡ዳዊት“Psalms of  David” (fols. <locus from="1r" to="99v"/>) I-<locus target="#2"/>) መኃልየ፡ነቢያት፡ ወጸሎቱ፡ ለሙሴ “The Canticles of the Prophets and the Prayer of Moses” (fols. <locus from="100r" to="110r"/>) I-<locus target="#3"/>) መኃልየ፡መኃልይ፡ዝውእቱ፡ዘሰሎሞን“Song of Songs of Solomon” (fols. <locus from="110v" to="115v"/>) I-<locus target="#4"/>) ውዳሴ፡ማርያም“The Praise of Mary” (fols. <locus from="116ra" to="126rb"/>) </p>
                     <p>I-<locus target="#5"/>) አንቀጸ፡ብርሃን“Gate of Light” (fols. <locus from="126rb" to="130vb"/>)</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
                
               </msContents>
